# Cloudflare Pages _redirects — read once per request at the edge.
#
# Bounce any direct hit on the canonical *.pages.dev hostname to the
# real custom domain so users always end up on periscope.thamibn.com
# regardless of how the link was shared. Path + query are preserved
# via :splat. 301 = permanent, cached by browsers + intermediaries.
#
# Requests for periscope.thamibn.com don't match this rule and are
# served normally; only the .pages.dev origin triggers the bounce.

https://php-periscope-docs.pages.dev/* https://periscope.thamibn.com/:splat 301
